      public void testSaveGuitarService()
      Tests saving a guitar service. Mocks the repository's save method to return the saved guitar service. Verifies the service calls the repository's save method and returns the same guitar service object.

    • testSaveGuitarServices

      public void testSaveGuitarServices()
      Tests saving a list of guitar services. Mocks repository's saveAll method to return the list. Verifies the service calls saveAll and returns the same list.

    • testGetGuitarServices

    • testGetGuitarServiceById

      public void testGetGuitarServiceById()

    • testGetGuitarServiceByType

      public void testGetGuitarServiceByType()

    • testUpdateGuitarService

      public void testUpdateGuitarService()
      Tests updating a GuitarService in the repository. Mocks findById and save methods of the repository. Verifies successful update by comparing retrieved GuitarService with the updated version. Also verifies that findById and save were called with appropriate arguments.

    • testDeleteGuitarService

      public void testDeleteGuitarService()
      Tests deleting a GuitarService by ID from the repository. Mocks deleteById to perform no action (void method). Verifies that the deletion message returned by the service matches the expected success message. Also verifies that deleteById was called with the provided ID.
